<p>As of now on the Allakhazam database there are 2 16 Damage Rogue Usable Piercers.   <br /> <br />Khalshazar <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=13250" title="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=13250" target="akztarg">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=13250</a> <br />and  <br />Bloodbath <a href="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=13241" title="http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=13241" target="akztarg">http://everquest.allakhazam.com/db/item.html?item=13241</a> <br /> <br />Both are vastly better than the epic, IF you have a similar haste item in your inventory (40%+) and even if you don't, their effects, procs, and ratios make them superior. Both drop in Ssraeshza Temple. <br /> <br />There are about (15) 15damage piercers in the database, including the epic.  There may be more undiscovered in PoP. <br /> <br />There are currently none above 16 damage, to my knowledge.  The reason for this is that beyond that damage, a Rogue could easily outdamage even the best Wizzy DD Spell with a simple attack that refreshed every 6 seconds or so.  Can you imagine the complaints?   <br /> <br /><em class="fs8">Edited, Wed Nov 13 01:53:09 2002</em></p>
